  "body": "Current blockers on this are @truffle/db's pouchdb's webSQL adapter dependency.\r\n\r\n> It's all kinds of broken.\r\nâ€“ @gnidan, 2022\r\n\r\nPossible resolution is to skip the db tests on Node v18, as truffle db is option. Of course this isn't preferred, as we do want @truffle/db to work on all versions of Node we support.\r\n\r\nWe should look into Ganache's [custom script](https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache/blob/5c57c22cae48df59f893ee76f19378b9594cceb9/scripts/require-engines.ts) that can [be used to skip tests](https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache/blob/5c57c22cae48df59f893ee76f19378b9594cceb9/src/chains/filecoin/filecoin/package.json#L33) based on a package.json's `engines` semver range.",
